title: 135: NFL's elite and 2017 NFL Draft
itunes:title: 135: NFL's elite and 2017 NFL Draft
description:
Former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks break down the close contests of Week 10 of the NFL as the playoff picture begins to take shape. The duo also discuss which college players are seeing their stock rising and falling.
